article_id:2740,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue on Android devices,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where the screen may freeze while playing quests on Android devices.</div><div><br></div><div>To alleviate this issue, tap the &quot;Enable Minimal Mode&quot; button in the System section of the Options screen, or tap &quot;Clear Cache&quot; from Menu on the title screen.</div><div><br></div><div>Any further updates regarding this issue will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1640683800,update_time1640682955